I went to  The Good Fork this past weekend  -Never been to Red Hook before- Just found this place walking around-  I was by myself - Had a great time-!!!!! The food is really farm fresh - melts in your mouth - Had tasty butternut squash appetizer dish and a great pasta dish- The pasta was one of the best I ever had !!!- The food is delicious -food presentation was beautiful  Great service - Friendly bartender (I ate at the bar -the  owner was also very hospitable-  Go and check it out for yourself !!!!!!!= Marilyn from Manhattan
